@Robb, my entire suggestion is that we lynch Eggman -&gt; Creature. My ordering makes more sense because I don't have a case against Creature if it turns out that Eggman is town.<br>
<br>
@Dwlee fucking well spotted lol.

@Rob, go ahead and add me to your scum list right below all of creature, Eggman and Crazy, in fact move your vote to me as well, because your logic basically condemns anyone who plays differently from game to game, and I know for a fact that my play is far more inconsistent than any player in this entire game.. <br>
<br>
